        "facts": "<p>Interpretation:</p>\n<table border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\"><strong>PRIEST Score</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\"><strong>30-day probability of adverse outcome</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">0-1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">1%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">2-3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">2%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">4*</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">3%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">9%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">15%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">18%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">22%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">9</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">26%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">10</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">29%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">11</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">34%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">12</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">38%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">13</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">46%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">14</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">47%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">15</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">49%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">16</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">55%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">17-25</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">59-88%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.565%;\">&ge;26</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.662%;\">&gt;99%</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>*Score &gt;4 predict adverse outcomes (defined as death or major organ support - respiratory, cardiovascular, or renal) with high sensitivity (98%) and low specificity (34%).</p>\n<p>From <a href=\"https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0245840\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Goodacre 2021</a>.</p>",
